            <title>[LU-15854] Add OST version check in sanity test 64 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15854</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;test_64h and test_64i have improper OST version checks which cause test failure in interop testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll push a patch that fixed that:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add a missing OST version check in test_64h (&lt;a href=&quot;#/c/43375/14/lustre/tests/sanity.sh])&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;this was spotted by Andreas after review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add the proper OST version check for test_64i (bump +1)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


